public static sealed interface ValueLayout.OfBoolean extends ValueLayoutPREVIEW
OfBoolean is a preview API of the Java platform.
Programs can only use OfBoolean when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.
A value layout whose carrier is boolean.class.
